<HEADLINE>
 
</HEADLINE>
  (For use by New York Times News
 Service clients) 
  
<TEXT>
<P>
   The following Arizona Republic story has been added for use by
clients of the NYTimes News Service for Monday, Nov. 1. If you have
any questions, please contact the Repub lic News Desk at (602)
444-8286.
</P>
<P>
   &QL; 
FREUD (undated) This November marks the 100th anniversary of
Sigmund Freud's revolutionary book, ``The Interpretation of
Dreams,'' that sent a shock wave through Western culture. What is
Freud's legacy today? By KEN LaFAVE. Story will move in the ``A,''
``K,'' and ``L'' categories. &QL;
</P>
