<P>
   A New Protest In Tiananmen Square
</P>
<P>
   They looked like dazed tourists in tennis shoes, but the
appearance on Tiananmen Square of clusters of Falun Gong believers
was a sign that the campaign to crush the popular spiritual
movement was in trouble.
</P>
<P>
   Those venturing onto the square for certain arrest were just
