<HEADLINE>
IN POLITICS, ETHNIC POSTURING ISN'T SIMPLE ANYMORE 
</HEADLINE>
  
(Repeating for all needing.) (The Week in Review) 
(bl) 
 By ADAM NAGOURNEY   
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   NEW YORK _ It once seemed so easy. Toward the end of every
