   SPORTS BUDGET OFFERS:
</P>
<P>
   PAYNE. Memorial for Payne Stewart in his hometown, Springfield,
Mo.
</P>
<P>
   NBAPREV. This NBA season will start on time, and that's pretty
much all we know about the league going into tonight's tipoff. The
recovery of Knicks center Patrick Ewing, the liver transplant
performed on the Spurs' Sean Elliott and the final season for
Charles Barkley have dominated the headlines during the off-season.
Out of the ashes, who will rise to the top remains a big question.
Could it finally be the Lakers, the team that imploded in the
playoffs last season? Or the cardiac Pacers? We don't have a clue.
Blair Kerkhoff. 20-22.
