<DOCNO> NYT19991101.0205 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-01 16:07 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5275 &Cx1f; tic-z
r a BC-FREUD-AZR &LR;      11-01 1566
</HEADER>
