   CRASH-PEOPLE (Washington) _ Egyptair's manifest tells no stories
about the people in the almost-full Flight 990. That was left to
friends and relatives, who recounted fascinating everyday stories
that reveal character. By John Donnelly. 1000 words.
</P>
