<HEADLINE>
HOT TRAVEL DEALS 
</HEADLINE>
  (For release Sun., Nov. 7) 
(jt) 
 By JANET PIORKO    
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   EARLY TO CRUISE _ The Delta Queen Steamboat Co. has an early
booking discount of $800 a couple for next year's trips on its
newest riverboat, the 161-passenger Columbia Queen, which is
scheduled to make its debut March 31 in the Pacific Northwest. The
offer applies to cruises throughout 2000 booked with a deposit six
months or more in advance. The Columbia Queen will make seven-night
cruises on the Columbia, Snake and Willamette Rivers traveling from
Portland, Ore., to Astoria, Ore., and then eastward to Lewiston,
Idaho. Rates range from $1,985 to $2,985 a person, double
occupancy, before the discount, and include many shore excursions
and a night's hotel stay in Portland, but not port charges and
taxes. Air fare is extra. Information: (800) 297-3960. On the
Internet: www.columbiaqueen.com.
</P>
<P>
   PARIS IN THE FALL _ A Celebrate Paris package, including air
fare from New York and five nights' hotel for $469 a person, double
occupancy, is offered by New Frontiers, the U.S. division of a
French travel company. The package is available from Nov. 1 through
March 31 (with a $200 surcharge for travel between Dec. 15 and Jan.
3); accommodations are in the 41-room Comfort Inn Sacre Coeur on
the Rue des Abbesses in Montmartre, and the package includes daily
Continental breakfast and airport transfers. Flights are on
Continental Airlines. Hotel upgrades are available. Information:
(800) 677-0720, or on the Internet: www.newfrontiers.com.
</P>
<P>
   ISRAEL PACKAGES _ Isram World of Travel has Priceless Israel
packages that start at $689 a person, double occupancy, including
air fare on El Al from New York to Tel Aviv; five nights' lodging,
daily buffet breakfasts and taxes. The $689 price is for
accommodations at the Sheraton Four Points Hotel in Jerusalem, and
is good from Nov. 21 to Dec. 23 and Jan. 4 to March 1; for $799,
the package includes lodging at the Dan Panorama Hotel in Tel Aviv
or Jerusalem, or a combination of the two, and is offered Nov. 16
to Dec. 23 and Jan. 6 to March 1. Departures from New York are
Sunday through Wednesday. Information: (800) 223-7460 or on the
Internet: www.isram.com.
</P>
<P>
   SPRING CREEK SKIING _ Spring Creek Ranch in Jackson Hole, Wyo.,
has a Ski Free Package through Dec. 24 starting at $140 a night for
two people in a room. The package includes a room with fireplace,
breakfast for two and a lift ticket to Jackson Hole or Grand
Targhee (limit one per person daily). Jackson Hole Mountain Resort
is set to open Dec. 4; Grand Targhee Resort, 42 miles from Jackson
Hole, Nov. 19. The 1,000-acre ranch has 36 guest rooms in addition
to lodgings ranging from studios to individual houses. Information
and reservations: (800) 443-6139. On the Internet:
www.springcreekresort.com.
</P>
<P>
