<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-11-01 20:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5701 &Cx1f; taf-z
u k BC-COLLINS-COLUMN-NYT &LR;      11-01 0763
