   (NYT31) ABOARD MERCHANT MARINE TRAINING SHIP KINGS POINTER,
South of Nantucket Island -- Nov. 1, 1999 -- AIRCRASH-10, 11-01 --
Debris from EgyptAir Flight 990 lies aboard the Merchant Marine
training ship after it was recovered on Sunday from the ocean south
of Nantucket Island. Coast Guard search crews gave up hope on
Monday of finding anyone alive from the doomed flight, but found a
large piece of wreckage and detected a signal believed to be from
