<TEXT>
<P>
   BC-CONGRESS-CENSUS-NYT (moved on Saturday, Oct. 30)
</P>
<P>
   A New York Times News Service article sent on Saturday, Oct. 30,
about the 2000 census referred incorrectly in some editions to a
recent series of joint news conferences by Democrats and
Republicans on statistical sampling. While the Republicans oppose
the technique, the Democrats favor it.
</P>
</TEXT>
